green onions and peanuts.

00:04:08.789 --> 00:04:10.411
So I don't think I've
ever had the combination

00:04:10.411 --> 00:04:12.639
of scallops and peanuts,

00:04:12.639 --> 00:04:16.264
so I am looking forward to this one.

00:04:16.264 --> 00:04:18.676
I'm not sure if you should
just go in with your face,

00:04:18.676 --> 00:04:20.387
or eat--
but anyways,

00:04:20.387 --> 00:04:23.970
I guess I'll go with
the fork method first,

00:04:26.211 --> 00:04:27.777
try to scoop on all those peanuts.

00:04:27.777 --> 00:04:28.610
Okay.

00:04:33.502 --> 00:04:34.335
Mmmmm.

00:04:36.968 --> 00:04:37.801
Oh yeah.

00:04:41.558 --> 00:04:43.131
Oh that really works,

00:04:43.131 --> 00:04:44.521
oh that really works well.

00:04:44.521 --> 00:04:45.591
And then you're supposed to chase it

00:04:45.591 --> 00:04:48.758
with the Vietnamese coriander as well.

00:04:50.731 --> 00:04:51.668
And I'm just gonna--

00:04:51.668 --> 00:04:53.693
I think I'm just gonna bite
straight into this shell

00:04:53.693 --> 00:04:55.526
to get everything out.

00:05:02.715 --> 00:05:03.548
Mmmmm.

00:05:05.649 --> 00:05:09.412
Oh, I think there must
be some butter on that

00:05:09.412 --> 00:05:11.594
because it tastes so good.

00:05:11.594 --> 00:05:12.427
Oh, wow.

00:05:14.439 --> 00:05:16.034
That is a combination,

00:05:16.034 --> 00:05:20.060
scallops and peanuts, that I
never would have thought of.

00:05:20.060 --> 00:05:21.273
And it doesn't--

00:05:21.273 --> 00:05:23.247
