00:05:23.247 --> 00:05:25.111
But it's actually amazing.

00:05:25.111 --> 00:05:28.420
It has that beautiful
sweetness from the scallop,

00:05:28.420 --> 00:05:31.232
and then that peanutty nutty flavor,

00:05:31.232 --> 00:05:34.762
and then also the
crunchiness from the peanuts.

00:05:34.762 --> 00:05:36.471
That is awesome.

00:05:36.471 --> 00:05:38.821
That's like a scallop with peanut butter.

00:05:38.821 --> 00:05:39.654
Amazing.

